{"tid":1615742,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢排打機領悟到一樣嘢","createTime":"2019-10-03T07:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T08:04:55.000Z","uid":198685,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"11861fdad6c53794c567a679e36d779bd1078792","tid":1615742,"uid":198685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:45:34.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無玩過LOL，有時明明自己友五個人見到對面得兩個都唔開佢波。當然啦，佢地唔搞我地我地都無謂開佢波，繼續推塔就得，始終都係一隻推塔game。<br />\n<br />\n但係玩左咁耐，成日見到自己人多過對面，對面開我地波，我地都會向後退。咁樣一個一個輪流捉，人多都比對面捉曬。雖然，我明白對面啲裝勁過我地，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係明明人多對面就會開始驚。只要我地衝翻轉頭，佢地甚至會退</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，我希望咁多位玩家要反打嘅時候，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就一齊上</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">對面捉極有限</span>。<br />\n就算你俾人捉到，隊友都可以幫你！你諗吓對面比咁多人圍，佢會繼續同你玩定走？<br />\n<br />\n以後大家打LOL嘅時候動作可以一致啲！唔好落單，咁就容易打Rk升分！上之前同隊友溝通好！開咪大叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">：「一齊上」！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n祝大家升rank順利！一齊交流或者批評我講錯嘅地方"},{"pid":"5d8e0f5f47a0704c92ea17a24b565f07a3201ad9","tid":1615742,"uid":198685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:46:04.000Z","msg":"開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413e6ae576824f38ab2333c54170a22ff4f616fc","tid":1615742,"uid":198685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"大家點睇"},{"pid":"3e063e3837f0f314a3fad775b1dda0db093f960e","tid":1615742,"uid":198685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:46:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f23e475f7e7051c8b6701cfda299e10bf44e6c25","tid":1615742,"uid":198685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:46:51.000Z","msg":"賽季就完啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cla